headline: BASF (BASFY) Stock Jumps 10.9%: Will It Continue to Soar?
summary: BASF (BASFY) witnessed a jump in share price last session on above-average trading volume. The latest trend in earnings estimate revisions for the stock doesn't suggest further strength down the road.
